
This is a fork from openslam_gmapping at https://github.com/ros-perception/openslam_gmapping

Originally, this is a fork from gmapping at https://openslam.informatik.uni-freiburg.de/data/svn/gmapping/trunk/
It includes a few patches that could be pushed upstream if needed


Purpose of this repository is to break the jail of ROS.org.
Plain and Portable gmapping will be provided for the users of Linux, OSX, and Windows!